file.name: property-name-not-identifier-safe.yml
file.content:
---
# Not all object properties have names that are safe as identifiers
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Example
  version: '1.0.1'
paths:
  /test1:
    get:
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  a-hyphenated-property:
                    type: string
